data.description: Need room inside and outside? This 2052 sq.ft. home situated on appx 1.1 acres outside the city tax district will meet your needs. A rounded cement porch welcomes you into a spacious open floor plan with lots of possibilities for family living and entertaining. Primary suite is located on the left with the secondary bedrooms on the right providing ample privacy when guests stay. Other features include a formal dining room, fireplace, separate laundry room & pantry area with half bath, and a tile walk-in shower. On the outside there is a 34' long chicken coop which includes 8 divided coops on the sides with a waterline run to the area for convenience. There is a fenced in area the length of the house for pets or children in the back and a 10x10 dog pen on the side. You have plenty of room to roam on this country size lot. Make your appointment to see this great property today!
